---
import '../styles/global.css';
const title = 'Cookie Policy | Ads Calculator';
const description = 'Cookie Policy for Ads Calculator. Learn what cookies we use, why, and how you can manage your preferences.';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://adsroicalc.com/cookies" />
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8428748101355923" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-4 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="font-bold text-xl">Ads <span class="text-blue-600 italic">Calculator</span></a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline">← Back to calculator</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">1. What are cookies?</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help sites remember your preferences and gather anonymous statistics to improve the user experience.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">2. Cookies we use</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 mt-4">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                  <th class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 text-left">Cookie</th>
                  <th class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 text-left">Provider</th>
                  <th class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 text-left">Duration</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">_ga, _ga_*</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Google Analytics</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Anonymous usage statistics</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">2 years</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">_gcl_au</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Google AdSense</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Ad conversion tracking</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">3 months</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">DSID, IDE</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Google DoubleClick</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Personalized advertising</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">1 year</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">GTM-*</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Google Tag Manager</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Script management</td>
                  <td class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 py-2">Session</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">3. How to manage cookies</h2>
          <p>You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings. Here are direct links for major browsers:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Chrome</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Safari</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">4. Opt-out of personalized advertising</h2>
          <p>You can opt out of Google's personalized advertising by visiting:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Network Advertising Initiative opt-out</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">5. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@adsroicalc.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hello@adsroicalc.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-8 px-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p>© 2026 Ads Calculator. All rights reserved. |
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="/legal" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Legal Notice</a> |
        <a href="/cookies" class="hover:text-blue-600 mx-2">Cookie Policy</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
